B.a6_=new A.iT("Delivery App","Pre-alpha version of a non-published delivery app. As the senior and sole Flutter developer, I spent one week developing an application to meet the specific requirements of a delivery service application. This involved customizing and enhancing the app to align with the customer's needs. Unfortunately, the project was never completed due to financial constraints.",null,B.Pi)
